                            <comment id="18568" author="costin" created="Thu, 13 Jul 2006 03:04:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;replied on the forum - basically adding an interceptor to do the translation from the cglib enhanced name to the original name should cleanup the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
